{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Shopify Design Challenge â€“ Exit Sign","content":"<p>\t\t\t\tThis week&#8217;s design challenge was to create a monster-themed exit sign for the new Lounge area at the Shopify office. I managed to win the challenge this week (woo!) ðŸ˜€ </p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s my entry:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/it_lurks_poster.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/it_lurks_poster.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"it_lurks_poster\" width=\"906\" height=\"1371\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2266\" srcset=\"http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/it_lurks_poster.jpg 906w, http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/it_lurks_poster-198x300.jpg 198w, http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/it_lurks_poster-768x1162.jpg 768w, http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/it_lurks_poster-677x1024.jpg 677w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 906px) 100vw, 906px\" /></a></p>\n<p>I get to hold on to this badboy for a couple of weeks:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/shopify-belt.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/shopify-belt-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"shopify belt\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2261\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"sub\">Shopify Design Challenge winner belt</div>\n<p><!--more--></p>\n<p>Below is one of my later sketches. I decided to ditch the nostrils because it made him look too &#8216;piggish&#8217;. Wish I had time to play around with shading and more details, maybe I&#8217;ll do that over the weekend or something.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/poster2.jpeg\"><img src=\"http://localhost:9999/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/poster2-1024x787.jpg\" alt=\"sketch for poster\" title=\"sketch for poster\" width=\"1024\" height=\"787\" class=\"size-large wp-image-2258\" /></a></p>\n","wordpress_id":2254},"allWordpressWpComments":{"ed